{"tid":2302443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國男子臉部畸形，靠才華迎娶美女大學生，孩子出生後笑不出來了","createTime":"2020-11-27T06:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T11:48:52.000Z","uid":25345,"like":20,"dislike":136,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab3f4947b7dfc5d681503f88544c385af79385e","tid":2302443,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"想必大家都知道，現在結婚前都要進行婚檢。如果體內攜帶遺傳病，不適合結婚的，將無法領到結婚證。這一方面是為了結婚的兩人負責，另一方面也是為了下一代考慮。而英國有名男子，因為家族遺傳病天生臉部畸形，靠自己的才華吸引了美麗的妻子。婚後，醫生本不建議二人生孩子，但他們卻不聽勸阻，最終自嘗苦果。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2Ffec4fe2cb2cd6b671cdfaff3ed8c2c89.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252Ffec4fe2cb2cd6b671cdfaff3ed8c2c89.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b489b71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  裡昂是英國曼徹斯特人，因為他的父母是近親結婚，所以導致他們兄弟姐妹都帶有遺傳病&mdash;&mdash;先天性顱骨畸形。這是胎兒在生長發育的時候，受遺傳因素導致顱骨發生變化的一種疾病，一般需要通過手術來進行治療。由於裡昂出生時還沒有有效的治療手段，所以他和兄弟姐妹們的臉部一直保持著畸形狀態，讓人看起來不太適應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2F4173d7d25f9cb62997ef31415b96f91b.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252F4173d7d25f9cb62997ef31415b96f91b.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=8115adca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  但裡昂的父母卻給了他們一個充滿愛的家庭，鼓勵他們勇於面對生活的困境，將他們培養成樂觀自信的人。俗話說，自信的人最美麗。在父母的鼓勵下，裡昂打開內心的束縛，在課堂上踊躍回答問題，認真記筆記，成為老師和同學眼中的&ldquo;三好學生&rdquo;。不知大家是否有這樣的感覺，當你與一個相貌不佳的人相處久了，就不會覺得他相貌有不適之處。因為你已感到習慣。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2F39066c9a1532c43ade6a897bed8f6492.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252F39066c9a1532c43ade6a897bed8f6492.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=487a2363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  裡昂娶到美貌妻子<br />\n<br />\n  而裡昂身邊的人也一樣，因為他的優秀，已經遮掩了他樣貌上的缺陷。大家也不再將畸形的臉部當回事。裡昂在改變周圍人對自己的看法後，決定幫助其他殘疾人也走出生活的困境。所以上大學後，裡昂在熱心公益的同時，還一手創建了關愛殘疾人協會。他未來的妻子安娜便是在這個協會中認識的。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2F83fded9ec9d349b70a599fa9bd88b3df.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252F83fded9ec9d349b70a599fa9bd88b3df.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=7e67bf9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  裡昂與安娜<br />\n<br />\n  在裡昂的努力和影響下，越來越多的殘疾人和志願者加入關愛殘疾人協會。安娜是一位熱心公益的大學生，在上大學前就經常去看望孤寡老人。在裡昂組建關愛殘疾人協會後，她便加入其中，成為了這些人中的一份子。隨著工作中的朝夕相處，安娜漸漸被裡昂所吸引。這個外貌看起來不佳的男孩，內心卻樂觀自信，而且說話幽默風趣。<br />\n<br />\n  二人孩子出生<br />\n<br />\n  安娜認為一個男人更重要的是事業心以及人品，所以在經過認真考慮後便選擇了與裡昂在一起。對於安娜的選擇，連裡昂都感到很意外。但有人能看上自己，還是一位美女，他又豈會拒絕?當安娜將裡昂帶回家見父母時，毫無意外地遭到了父母的反對。安娜的父母認為，裡昂的長相很可能會影響下一代，他們無法接受這樣的女婿。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2F79aa0e8f6c9143975cad66cae05c0b3f.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252F79aa0e8f6c9143975cad66cae05c0b3f.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=31bee416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  裡昂與女兒<br />\n<br />\n  但安娜卻堅定地要與裡昂在一起，不惜和父母鬧翻。二人結婚後，生活得很幸福，裡昂也加倍對安娜好。不久之後，安娜告訴裡昂：&ldquo;我懷孕了!&rdquo;裡昂一聽要當爸爸了，欣喜若狂，立刻帶著妻子到醫院檢查。但醫生檢查後，卻建議他們放棄這個孩子，因為檢查結果顯示胎兒不正常。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.ws.126.net%2Fimg%2F07e41b08522a1b3f93af9bde4ef4f7b6.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fcrawl.ws.126.net%252Fimg%252F07e41b08522a1b3f93af9bde4ef4f7b6.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d5f9eb6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  裡昂與家人<br />\n<br />\n  裡昂為此感到感傷，安娜卻堅持生下來。結果等孩子出生後，二人還是沉默了。盡管他們早有准備，但看著女兒的樣貌，還是一陣心疼，原本歡樂的日子也笑不出來。但女兒已經出生，他們能做的，就是給女兒更多的保護，以及將她培養成一個自信的人。"},{"pid":"12aeaa6d4a08edb82e15fcdd88e43bd93d354bdd","tid":2302443,"uid":165336,"like":189,"dislike":4,"score":185,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"痴撚線生咁撚多個完全遺傳哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係害撚死下一代<br />\n好心佢收養算啦"},{"pid":"f92039ba868863d975654482e1a82c6b0ef7e72d","tid":2302443,"uid":14503,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:19:15.000Z","msg":"基因強大"},{"pid":"78a4c763f104420c16b327791a98bf7d3959381d","tid":2302443,"uid":155095,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"智力正常就去整容啦"},{"pid":"e16601884dcdd637a13012d49adf68de4e5000f3","tid":2302443,"uid":75823,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"成隻毛公仔樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce23b41b6cf0a4be448f11b2eb98777b359936b0","tid":2302443,"uid":54579,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"呢d真係仆街黎，幾撚有錢都冇用"},{"pid":"74099858c6ca480f623a8747af5fd2e4f9212a33","tid":2302443,"uid":8776,"like":37,"dislike":4,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhLhgPP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfhLhgPP.jpg&h=be6059c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e3d269377f6d50b761009ac5bc007970f04635f","tid":2302443,"uid":8681,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"好似樹懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a9b1f3512ad9f27080071857fc0971f8b2a3e1","tid":2302443,"uid":263297,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:21:30.000Z","msg":"話我冷血都好,有遺傳病真係唔好有下一代<br />\n辛苦仔女又辛苦自己,簡直係折磨"},{"pid":"2952d05d2af3594bff60e3715ca673b24f17a758","tid":2302443,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5766536b350b6ee33902b957d3107213adc008","tid":2302443,"uid":27077,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"唔驚走散"},{"pid":"0f40dd4a84c4fc1d0a0e88b449b2c286dd011388","tid":2302443,"uid":66365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:22:13.000Z","msg":"Wrong Turn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8e6a8ea5b9b03baa059615b1824b9c68387938","tid":2302443,"uid":54927,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"好心立法呢啲仆街唔准生啦"},{"pid":"9aa84c95611f55b1ef437a28f7c98545cf73d6c2","tid":2302443,"uid":47239,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:22:35.000Z","msg":"咁似Content farm"},{"pid":"86aac5b232c40ffa29d911569ddc8a85c2b85893","tid":2302443,"uid":55458,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"咁都屌到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a508a3788f